    dc:creator "Das, Indraneil; Lyngdoh, Ronald K.; Rangad, Duwaki; Hooroo, Rupa N. K." ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from the sacred groves of Mawphlang, Meghalaya, north-eastern India" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275531> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275531>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitat and microhabitat of Leptolalax khasiorum sp. nov. at Mawphlang, Meghalaya State, north-eastern India. A. Mawphalang, a sacred grove protected by the Khasi tribe; B. Microhabitat at the time of sampling in the month of March was moist interstices of rocks along an intermittent hill stream within a subtropical wet hill forest." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275531/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

